1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:01,910
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,910 --> 00:00:03,540
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:05,110
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,510 --> 00:00:08,150
(Kim Myung Hui, Jung Yoon Jung,
Park Min Jun, Park Tae Ho)

5
00:00:08,150 --> 00:00:09,780
(Oh Jung Ran, Song Geun Tae,
Choi Sam Sik, Choi Yu Na)

6
00:00:16,450 --> 00:00:17,720
(Episode 16)

7
00:00:20,160 --> 00:00:21,890
When dawn breaks
and you enter Adele,

8
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:26,030
an all-out war with everyone here
will begin.

9
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:30,440
The ones fighting will be
Park Tae Ho and Choi Yu Na.

10
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:35,070
I'll make them destroy each other...

11
00:00:36,210 --> 00:00:37,580
with the very hands they joined...

12
00:00:38,080 --> 00:00:39,910
to kill my father.

13
00:00:42,680 --> 00:00:44,280
To do that,
you need to protect yourself first.

14
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:48,020
That starts with fooling everyone
on this board.

15
00:00:49,590 --> 00:00:50,790
I've been preparing for a long time.

16
00:00:53,390 --> 00:00:56,030
I've already fully become Chloe.

17
00:00:57,760 --> 00:00:59,430
Even with thorough
long-term preparation,

18
00:00:59,430 --> 00:01:00,470
it can still be difficult.

19
00:01:05,700 --> 00:01:08,010
(Kim Myung Hui, Adele, Director)

20
00:01:11,910 --> 00:01:14,410
You need to be especially careful
with these two.

21
00:01:15,380 --> 00:01:17,080
Not Choi Yu Na and Park Tae Ho,

22
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:18,820
but those two?

23
00:01:18,950 --> 00:01:22,590
That's right. One of them...

24
00:01:22,650 --> 00:01:24,060
could be either an ally or an enemy.

25
00:01:24,590 --> 00:01:25,860
And the other...

26
00:01:27,790 --> 00:01:29,530
will make you most vulnerable.

27
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,660
He has the power
to bring out Baek Jin Ju...

28
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:34,300
inside Chloe.

29
00:01:52,850 --> 00:01:54,390
Do you happen to believe in fate?

30
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:55,820
No.

31
00:01:56,190 --> 00:01:57,960
I don't believe in things like that.

32
00:01:58,460 --> 00:01:59,460
Then,

33
00:02:01,190 --> 00:02:02,260
just this once,

34
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,200
may I hold you?

35
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:07,800
Excuse me?

36
00:02:23,950 --> 00:02:27,120
You keep telling me I'm wrong,

37
00:02:28,650 --> 00:02:29,650
but my eyes,

38
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,890
my hands, and my heart...

39
00:02:33,530 --> 00:02:35,030
know what they feel.

40
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:39,330
Are you not telling the truth,

41
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:42,200
or is my heart wrong?

42
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,310
Jin Ju.

43
00:03:03,390 --> 00:03:04,590
Why is Min Jun...

44
00:03:12,860 --> 00:03:14,300
Just as James feared,

45
00:03:14,970 --> 00:03:16,970
they're the two
I need to be most wary of.

46
00:03:18,270 --> 00:03:19,270
In some ways,

47
00:03:19,940 --> 00:03:23,010
they're the two
I need to deceive the most.

48
00:03:35,450 --> 00:03:38,590
Right. I need to show them
the perfect lie...

49
00:03:39,390 --> 00:03:40,930
that I'm the perfect Chloe.

50
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,360
Jin Ju?

51
00:03:46,130 --> 00:03:47,630
I guess there was a woman
by that name.

52
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:51,800
And it seems you two didn't part
on good terms.

53
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,010
Did she die or something?

54
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:06,080
I finally get it.

55
00:04:07,020 --> 00:04:09,550
That's why everyone looked like
they'd seen a ghost.

56
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,090
Do I really...

57
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:14,790
look that much like this dead woman?

58
00:04:20,930 --> 00:04:23,640
So what is it that you want from me?

59
00:04:24,540 --> 00:04:26,870
Am I supposed to take her place,
letting you hold me,

60
00:04:27,740 --> 00:04:29,110
and holding you in return?

61
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:40,420
I've no interest in being
a replacement for a dead girl.

62
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:43,190
How about...

63
00:04:44,460 --> 00:04:46,190
having some fun with me instead?

64
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:48,230
It can be casual,

65
00:04:50,330 --> 00:04:51,760
but I'd prefer hot and heavy.

66
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:54,270
What do you say?

67
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,870
No,

68
00:04:58,700 --> 00:04:59,840
I was just...

69
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:06,580
Mr. Park.

70
00:05:08,210 --> 00:05:11,050
Dead women don't come back to life.

71
00:05:12,650 --> 00:05:13,650
Love...

72
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:15,220
and fate.

73
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,960
None of that stuff has
any real power.

74
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,240
I...

75
00:05:34,370 --> 00:05:35,610
seem to have been mistaken.

76
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:40,140
I'm sorry for crossing the line.

77
00:06:13,610 --> 00:06:16,010
Executive Director Park is my son,

78
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:19,880
so I'm going to need an explanation
for what just happened.

79
00:06:20,990 --> 00:06:22,950
I don't think the situation calls
for an explanation.

80
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:25,260
What you saw is what happened.

81
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:29,190
We met,
became interested in each other,

82
00:06:29,590 --> 00:06:31,600
and were just testing
the waters physically...

83
00:06:31,930 --> 00:06:33,930
to see if we could get closer.

84
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:39,600
But you're glaring at me
like I did something wrong.

85
00:06:40,770 --> 00:06:44,440
Because that kind of behavior
is unacceptable here at Adele Group.

86
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:48,210
Director Park is engaged,

87
00:06:48,810 --> 00:06:50,410
and his fiancee
is Team Leader Choi Yu Na.

88
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:54,720
To prevent any rumors or disruption
at the company,

89
00:06:55,820 --> 00:06:57,820
please be more careful
going forward.

90
00:06:58,390 --> 00:07:01,260
Understood. May I go now?

91
00:07:08,100 --> 00:07:09,270
Right.

92
00:07:11,300 --> 00:07:14,470
For someone about to get married,

93
00:07:14,910 --> 00:07:16,370
he doesn't seem happy at all.

94
00:07:19,540 --> 00:07:21,380
Are you really planning...

95
00:07:21,910 --> 00:07:23,710
to go through with this marriage?

96
00:07:36,130 --> 00:07:38,830
Who are you, really?

97
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:42,100
Will you be an asset to my plan,

98
00:07:42,370 --> 00:07:44,640
or will you get in my way?

99
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:49,870
There's only one reason
behind every choice I make.

100
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:54,580
My priority is protecting my son
and Adele Group.

101
00:07:56,850 --> 00:07:59,420
I don't want to regret
partnering with you,

102
00:08:00,150 --> 00:08:01,550
so I expect your full cooperation.

103
00:08:04,090 --> 00:08:05,460
Protecting,

104
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,330
partnering,

105
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:08,690
and expecting cooperation.

106
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:11,460
You can dress it up
with pretty words,

107
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:14,970
but what you really mean is,
"Stay out of my way."

108
00:08:17,770 --> 00:08:20,000
Got it. Message received.

109
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:23,570
In fact, thanks to you,

110
00:08:24,210 --> 00:08:25,840
I know exactly
what I need to do now.

111
00:08:26,580 --> 00:08:27,580
Well then.

112
00:08:28,550 --> 00:08:30,410
(Jewelry Division,
Director Kim Myung Hui)

113
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:43,730
Chloe...

114
00:08:46,830 --> 00:08:48,130
So, her name's Chloe.

115
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:50,500
It's Jin Ju.

116
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:52,940
Others might not realize it,

117
00:08:55,210 --> 00:08:56,370
but I can tell.

118
00:09:04,420 --> 00:09:07,250
Are you really Min Jun's friend?

119
00:09:08,490 --> 00:09:10,220
Well, you see...

120
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,190
It's a pleasure to meet you.

121
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:16,560
I'm Chloe.

122
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,330
I know it too.

123
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:24,170
Chloe, or whoever you are,
I know in my bones...

124
00:09:25,470 --> 00:09:26,970
I can't let you slip away.

125
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,680
I don't want to hesitate
like last time...

126
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,710
and end up regretting it.

127
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:55,600
So, when you said
we should become in-laws...

128
00:09:55,730 --> 00:09:59,640
Honestly, I just feel
so bad for you.

129
00:10:00,370 --> 00:10:02,770
If your daughter is marrying
into the Adele family,

130
00:10:02,770 --> 00:10:04,540
she should choose
the legitimate son.

131
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:08,610
But we...

132
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:12,220
Of course, I'm well aware
of your family's situation.

133
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:15,420
You're not from a wealthy
or prestigious family.

134
00:10:15,950 --> 00:10:17,560
You didn't dare go after Hyun Jun...

135
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:21,190
because he was way out
of your "tree."

136
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:23,790
What was that?

137
00:10:24,460 --> 00:10:26,730
Since the real prize
was out of reach,

138
00:10:26,730 --> 00:10:28,770
you took the consolation prize.

139
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:31,770
That's why you latched onto Min Jun.

140
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:35,110
So, out of the goodness of my heart,
I'll give you a chance.

141
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:38,680
Forget the consolation prize
and go for the jackpot.

142
00:10:39,210 --> 00:10:41,580
Ditch the chicken for a pheasant.

143
00:10:41,780 --> 00:10:42,850
But...

144
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,580
You see,

145
00:10:47,220 --> 00:10:50,620
we don't discriminate
between pheasants and chickens.

146
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:53,160
I mean,
who are you to discriminate...

147
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:55,560
against people in this day and age?

148
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:56,890
How tacky.

149
00:11:02,470 --> 00:11:04,770
Did she just call me classless?

150
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:09,440
You think we're not wealthy
or prestigious enough?

151
00:11:11,710 --> 00:11:12,780
One more thing.

152
00:11:13,810 --> 00:11:15,750
I may not care about much else,

153
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:19,750
but there is one thing I look for
in my child's in-laws.

154
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,320
Really?

155
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:23,990
So tell me,

156
00:11:24,590 --> 00:11:27,160
what does someone so cultured
and non-discriminatory value?

157
00:11:27,220 --> 00:11:28,560
The groom's mother's character.

158
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:30,730
Honey, please.

159
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:33,660
What was that?

160
00:11:33,730 --> 00:11:37,270
The other potential mother-in-law?
She's a pheasant...

161
00:11:37,330 --> 00:11:40,740
No, scratch that.
She's like a graceful phoenix.

162
00:11:40,810 --> 00:11:41,910
But as for you...

163
00:11:49,610 --> 00:11:51,550
What about me?

164
00:11:52,050 --> 00:11:53,850
What would you say I am?

165
00:11:55,690 --> 00:11:57,190
Way out of our "tree?"

166
00:11:58,020 --> 00:12:00,790
Just so you know,
it's league, not "tree."

167
00:12:01,430 --> 00:12:02,660
- Hey!
- Goodness.

168
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:06,130
- Are you kidding me?
- My gosh!

169
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:08,500
- Get over here!
- Have you lost your mind?

170
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:10,270
- Hey!
- Please don't!

171
00:12:23,380 --> 00:12:25,150
(Consultant, Chloe Lee)

172
00:12:25,950 --> 00:12:26,980
It can't be.

173
00:12:27,620 --> 00:12:29,520
There's no way Baek Jin Ju is alive.

174
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,200
It's Chairman Park Tae Ho!

175
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:49,110
She can't be alive.

176
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,510
Make sure you watch her closely.

177
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:55,680
And bring me proof
that Chloe is not Baek Jin Ju!

178
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,020
Right.

179
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:01,490
I need proof
that she's not Baek Jin Ju...

180
00:13:01,490 --> 00:13:03,250
so I can be sure too.

181
00:13:05,290 --> 00:13:07,220
But where am I supposed to find
that kind of proof?

182
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:10,630
It's not like
she has some kind of special mark.

183
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:32,050
You met Director Kim Myung Hui
on your own too?

184
00:13:32,680 --> 00:13:34,190
There's nothing to worry about.

185
00:13:35,090 --> 00:13:37,690
It actually helped me
confirm something.

186
00:13:40,990 --> 00:13:42,730
Director Kim Myung Hui
is definitely....

187
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:45,630
going to be a problem for us.

188
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:50,270
(Project Chloe File)

189
00:13:52,400 --> 00:13:55,770
Chloe will surely help
with our plan.

190
00:13:55,970 --> 00:13:57,040
Of course.

191
00:13:57,410 --> 00:13:59,940
She's a genius who turns
everything she touches to gold.

192
00:14:00,410 --> 00:14:03,410
If we revive and rebrand
the bio division,

193
00:14:03,680 --> 00:14:06,780
the chairman and the board
won't be able to push you around.

194
00:14:06,850 --> 00:14:10,050
It'll be your armor and weapons
in the succession battle.

195
00:14:11,190 --> 00:14:12,220
But...

196
00:14:28,670 --> 00:14:31,710
Because of Chloe,
even Min Jun wasn't himself.

197
00:14:32,180 --> 00:14:36,480
I still don't even know why
everyone's so fixated on her,

198
00:14:37,180 --> 00:14:39,620
so working with her makes me uneasy.

199
00:14:39,750 --> 00:14:42,490
But you can't just back out
of this partnership.

200
00:14:43,220 --> 00:14:45,520
Besides, wouldn't it
be better for Min Jun...

201
00:14:45,590 --> 00:14:47,020
if you gained more power...

202
00:14:47,020 --> 00:14:49,060
by successfully rebranding
the bio division?

203
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:52,060
Because then I'd be able
to oppose the marriage?

204
00:14:52,330 --> 00:14:54,030
This isn't just about you.

205
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:56,830
We need Chloe
for Min Jun's sake, too.

206
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:59,200
Even if it causes a bit of a stir.

207
00:15:01,540 --> 00:15:02,540
(Project Chloe File)

208
00:15:10,350 --> 00:15:11,920
(President Choi Sam Sik)

209
00:15:15,150 --> 00:15:17,660
Yes, this is Kim Myung Hui.
How can I help you?

210
00:15:20,090 --> 00:15:22,090
What? A fight?

211
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:27,630
It felt good to get
my blood pumping again.

212
00:15:28,300 --> 00:15:30,570
How dare she mess with me?

213
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:37,510
You're going to be
the death of me, I swear.

214
00:15:37,610 --> 00:15:38,980
If you went there to become family,

215
00:15:38,980 --> 00:15:40,310
you should've shown
more self-control.

216
00:15:40,380 --> 00:15:42,810
How are you going to deal
with the fallout from this?

217
00:15:52,260 --> 00:15:54,660
Fine, I pulled her hair.

218
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:56,590
So what?

219
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:59,930
I always knew you were greedy,
but I thought you had self-respect.

220
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:02,230
But this stunt you pulled?

221
00:16:03,930 --> 00:16:05,500
I guess I was completely mistaken.

222
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:08,010
What did you just say?

223
00:16:08,010 --> 00:16:10,970
You tried to steal my son's fiancee
and ended up in a catfight.

224
00:16:11,210 --> 00:16:13,810
And even after getting caught,
you still have no shame!

225
00:16:14,780 --> 00:16:16,410
Frankly, it's just pathetic.

226
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:20,050
Says the tramp
who weaseled her way in here.

227
00:16:20,180 --> 00:16:22,090
How dare you act superior...

228
00:16:22,090 --> 00:16:25,660
when you're using your own son
to steal from mine?

229
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:28,030
You know what?

230
00:16:28,160 --> 00:16:30,390
I might as well
rip your hair out too.

231
00:16:31,060 --> 00:16:34,400
I'll tear you to shreds today,
so bring it on!

232
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:36,730
No, wait. Just stop it.

233
00:16:36,800 --> 00:16:38,340
That's enough.

234
00:16:38,770 --> 00:16:40,740
If you so much
as touch Director Kim,

235
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:42,710
you'll be signing
your own death warrant.

236
00:16:43,210 --> 00:16:44,580
Tae Ho is about to...

237
00:16:46,010 --> 00:16:47,810
The chairman will be home soon.

238
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:49,610
If he finds out about this,

239
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:51,080
it'll be a disaster!

240
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:53,480
Then I'll just have to be quick.

241
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:55,590
Quick to finish what?

242
00:16:58,690 --> 00:16:59,760
Seriously?

243
00:17:00,160 --> 00:17:02,060
Why do you look so disheveled?

244
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:03,960
What have you gotten yourself
into this time?

245
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:07,460
Well, it's not what you think.

246
00:17:07,930 --> 00:17:08,930
We had...

247
00:17:09,670 --> 00:17:11,440
a bit of a disagreement.

248
00:17:12,370 --> 00:17:14,810
She kept telling me to hurry up
and set up Min Jun's marriage...

249
00:17:15,810 --> 00:17:18,980
because it's the only way
you'd consider Hyun Jun's.

250
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:23,480
I told her I'd handle
Min Jun's marriage myself...

251
00:17:24,250 --> 00:17:26,120
and that she should stay out of it.

252
00:17:26,580 --> 00:17:27,750
That's when things got heated.

253
00:17:28,520 --> 00:17:29,590
Is that true?

254
00:17:30,190 --> 00:17:32,020
Well...

255
00:17:33,660 --> 00:17:35,960
I was getting
a little impatient, that's all.

256
00:17:37,190 --> 00:17:40,400
You only think about yourself,
don't you?

257
00:17:40,630 --> 00:17:45,500
Stop bothering people
and stay out of it for once.

258
00:17:46,300 --> 00:17:47,540
Good grief.

259
00:17:48,270 --> 00:17:50,140
Myung Hui,
come with me for a moment.

260
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:56,710
Stay quiet
if you don't want him to find out.

261
00:17:57,150 --> 00:17:59,580
I'm not doing this for you.
I'm doing it for Min Jun.

262
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:02,420
I'm only holding back
so he doesn't get caught up in this.

263
00:18:11,930 --> 00:18:14,630
She thinks she's holding back?

264
00:18:14,930 --> 00:18:16,530
If I had my way,

265
00:18:16,600 --> 00:18:18,700
I'd have strangled her
a dozen times over by now.

266
00:18:19,170 --> 00:18:22,910
Tae Ho said that was the last straw,
and he'd even disown Hyun Jun.

267
00:18:22,970 --> 00:18:25,110
That's why I'm letting you live!

268
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:31,680
Gosh, right.

269
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:33,180
So, about Chloe.

270
00:18:34,450 --> 00:18:38,290
Tell me exactly
how you convinced her...

271
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:40,020
to sign the contract.

272
00:18:41,430 --> 00:18:43,890
It was a standard
recruitment process.

273
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,830
I sent her a proposal,
she expressed her interest,

274
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:49,500
and we took it from there.

275
00:18:50,030 --> 00:18:51,030
Why do you ask?

276
00:18:51,370 --> 00:18:54,670
Are you unhappy with Chloe
now that you've met her?

277
00:18:56,970 --> 00:18:58,410
Why would I be?

278
00:18:59,040 --> 00:19:02,580
Everyone from reporters I know
to the heads of our rivals...

279
00:19:03,350 --> 00:19:05,380
is asking me how we landed Chloe.

280
00:19:06,320 --> 00:19:08,390
They're all blowing up my phone,
so I had to ask.

281
00:19:09,020 --> 00:19:11,760
It was good timing.
Chloe was looking for a new project,

282
00:19:11,820 --> 00:19:14,890
and she liked the proposal
we'd put together.

283
00:19:15,290 --> 00:19:16,360
A little luck didn't hurt either.

284
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:19,960
A little luck?

285
00:19:20,730 --> 00:19:24,070
Why don't you freshen up?
I'll have dinner ready.

286
00:19:24,840 --> 00:19:26,470
By the way, how's Min Jun?

287
00:19:29,270 --> 00:19:30,540
Did he say...

288
00:19:31,910 --> 00:19:33,440
anything else about Chloe?

289
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:38,050
You know what Min Jun is like.

290
00:19:39,020 --> 00:19:42,290
What would he say
about a new member of the team?

291
00:19:45,190 --> 00:19:47,190
If anything,

292
00:19:47,620 --> 00:19:49,630
I thought Ms. Choi
was acting a little odd.

293
00:19:51,060 --> 00:19:54,800
Right after seeing Chloe,
she ran out to get you herself.

294
00:19:55,530 --> 00:19:58,000
Was there a reason for that,

295
00:19:58,370 --> 00:20:00,500
or do they have a history
I don't know about?

296
00:20:07,810 --> 00:20:10,280
History? Don't be ridiculous.

297
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:13,820
I was told Chloe had arrived,

298
00:20:14,150 --> 00:20:15,990
so I went to see for myself.

299
00:20:16,190 --> 00:20:17,250
You can go now.

300
00:20:52,260 --> 00:20:53,260
Right.

301
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:56,790
If I let my guard down or hesitate,

302
00:20:57,890 --> 00:21:00,430
I'll lose everything to Oh Jung Ran.

303
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:17,880
Why did you come back
to the office this late?

304
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:22,420
My mind is racing,
so I thought I'd get some work done.

305
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:26,520
You never get a moment of peace,
thanks to Oh Jung Ran.

306
00:21:27,420 --> 00:21:29,890
I bet you're more comfortable here
than at home.

307
00:21:32,100 --> 00:21:34,400
We just finished setting up
your new office.

308
00:21:34,700 --> 00:21:35,700
What do you think?

309
00:21:36,130 --> 00:21:38,770
It must feel real now that
you're leading the bio division.

310
00:21:40,500 --> 00:21:41,510
It does.

311
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:43,870
When Chairman Park...

312
00:21:43,870 --> 00:21:45,680
makes you president, as he promised,

313
00:21:45,780 --> 00:21:50,480
that shiny nameplate is going
to look great on this desk.

314
00:21:52,180 --> 00:21:53,780
Don't you regret giving up...

315
00:21:54,350 --> 00:21:57,150
your work as a gemologist
and your role in the jewelry division?

316
00:21:59,220 --> 00:22:02,430
Getting into jewelry was just
a means to an end.

317
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:04,730
It was a way to be recognized...

318
00:22:04,730 --> 00:22:07,530
as an executive at Adele Group,
not just as the chairman's mistress.

319
00:22:09,270 --> 00:22:12,070
Once I earned that respect,
Min Jun would no longer be seen...

320
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:14,940
as the son of a mistress,

321
00:22:15,540 --> 00:22:18,280
but as a rightful heir
to Adele Group.

322
00:22:18,410 --> 00:22:22,380
Still, it feels like throwing away
the last 30 years of your life.

323
00:22:24,050 --> 00:22:27,580
Adele Group has changed a lot
over the past 30 years.

324
00:22:28,420 --> 00:22:30,250
Instead of staying stuck...

325
00:22:30,990 --> 00:22:33,620
in the jewelry business
like Chairman Park wants,

326
00:22:33,690 --> 00:22:37,090
it's better for me
to find a new path now.

327
00:22:37,490 --> 00:22:39,400
Besides, it's a chance...

328
00:22:39,500 --> 00:22:41,900
to carry on Dr. Baek's legacy
and build on it.

329
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:46,340
That's why I'm going to use Chloe.

330
00:22:47,970 --> 00:22:49,670
Even if it's still risky.

331
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:57,510
(Bion Tech)

332
00:23:00,080 --> 00:23:02,190
(Bion Tech)

333
00:23:07,760 --> 00:23:12,700
(Kim Myung Hui, Adele, Director)

334
00:23:24,710 --> 00:23:27,740
There's only one reason
behind every choice I make.

335
00:23:28,780 --> 00:23:32,380
My priority is protecting my son
and Adele Group.

336
00:23:34,250 --> 00:23:35,990
I hate to break it to you,

337
00:23:36,650 --> 00:23:38,920
but you won't be able
to protect anything.

338
00:23:40,360 --> 00:23:42,760
Because everything
you're trying to protect...

339
00:23:43,690 --> 00:23:45,360
will be shattered,

340
00:23:46,100 --> 00:23:48,800
destroyed, and used...

341
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:54,140
for my revenge.

342
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:00,440
(Park Min Jun)

343
00:24:15,860 --> 00:24:19,530
From now on, if you get bad ideas,
you come straight to me.

344
00:24:19,660 --> 00:24:24,400
I'll remind you
how precious and perfect you are.

345
00:24:24,670 --> 00:24:25,840
Do I really...

346
00:24:26,700 --> 00:24:28,570
look that much like this dead woman?

347
00:24:32,610 --> 00:24:34,610
I've no interest in being
a replacement for a dead girl.

348
00:24:36,210 --> 00:24:37,210
How about...

349
00:24:38,420 --> 00:24:40,350
having some fun with me instead?

350
00:24:40,750 --> 00:24:42,350
It can be casual,

351
00:24:44,250 --> 00:24:45,820
but I'd prefer hot and heavy.

352
00:24:47,220 --> 00:24:48,230
What do you say?

353
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:06,810
A day like this calls for a drink.

354
00:25:12,020 --> 00:25:13,380
It still wasn't her,
even on a second look, right?

355
00:25:14,320 --> 00:25:15,590
She's Chloe, end of story.

356
00:25:23,090 --> 00:25:24,160
Man, this is good.

357
00:25:26,060 --> 00:25:28,730
You'll see her daily from tomorrow.
Will you be okay?

358
00:25:29,630 --> 00:25:31,130
If it's awkward,
just stay out of her way.

359
00:25:32,170 --> 00:25:33,400
I'm not going to avoid her.

360
00:25:37,570 --> 00:25:40,440
It was only a second glance anyway.

361
00:25:41,910 --> 00:25:42,980
So?

362
00:25:43,280 --> 00:25:45,620
How many times
are you going to check?

363
00:25:48,420 --> 00:25:50,390
On the off chance
that she really is Jin Ju,

364
00:25:52,020 --> 00:25:53,520
I'll keep checking...

365
00:25:54,890 --> 00:25:56,790
until even that faint hope
is completely gone.

366
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:24,590
Should I just wait
until Min Jun gives up?

367
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:27,760
This time,

368
00:26:29,130 --> 00:26:31,090
with Chloe, not Baek Jin Ju,

369
00:26:35,270 --> 00:26:36,970
I want to be the first to have her.

370
00:26:45,010 --> 00:26:47,510
Where... Choi Yu Na!

371
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:50,510
You brat, are you going
to answer me or what?

372
00:26:50,650 --> 00:26:53,120
What's the deal with you
and Park Hyun Jun?

373
00:26:53,420 --> 00:26:54,680
What are you talking about?

374
00:26:55,050 --> 00:26:57,290
Me and that loser Park Hyun Jun?
As if.

375
00:26:57,550 --> 00:27:00,360
Well, Chairman Park's wife
came over today and...

376
00:27:00,420 --> 00:27:01,860
She may be tiny,

377
00:27:01,860 --> 00:27:04,460
but her grip
is surprisingly powerful.

378
00:27:04,560 --> 00:27:06,230
Where the heck is it?

379
00:27:06,530 --> 00:27:08,160
What are you looking for?

380
00:27:08,670 --> 00:27:09,730
- Here it is.
- Goodness.

381
00:27:10,800 --> 00:27:11,870
What's this?

382
00:27:12,370 --> 00:27:13,370
What?

383
00:27:13,840 --> 00:27:15,310
What are you looking for?

384
00:27:29,950 --> 00:27:32,160
- Here's your coffee.
- Thank you.

385
00:27:33,060 --> 00:27:36,090
I know almost all my regulars
who come by before work.

386
00:27:36,460 --> 00:27:37,960
This must be your first time here.

387
00:27:38,290 --> 00:27:39,300
Of course it is.

388
00:27:41,360 --> 00:27:42,970
Today's her first day on the job.

389
00:27:43,730 --> 00:27:45,900
On your very first day,

390
00:27:45,970 --> 00:27:48,940
you had the good sense to pick
the best cafe in the area.

391
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:52,080
Did you research Adele Group
even down to the coffee shops?

392
00:27:52,810 --> 00:27:54,410
You're starting at Adele Group?

393
00:27:55,310 --> 00:27:58,150
Congratulations.
Please come by often.

394
00:27:58,420 --> 00:27:59,420
- I will.
- Great.

395
00:28:06,890 --> 00:28:09,260
Don't tell me you already forgot me.

396
00:28:09,260 --> 00:28:10,760
We met yesterday.

397
00:28:11,530 --> 00:28:14,730
Of course not,
Director Park Hyun Jun.

398
00:28:15,800 --> 00:28:18,870
No way. I'm touched
you remembered my name.

399
00:28:19,270 --> 00:28:20,270
You...

400
00:28:22,010 --> 00:28:23,170
remembered me.

401
00:28:25,780 --> 00:28:29,050
You're giving me a strange look too.

402
00:28:29,850 --> 00:28:32,020
I heard I look like
a woman who died.

403
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:34,150
Is that why?

404
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:37,290
Are you checking
how similar we look?

405
00:28:38,390 --> 00:28:41,160
I'm trying to tell
how different you are.

406
00:28:49,570 --> 00:28:50,830
Just as I thought.

407
00:28:51,470 --> 00:28:53,070
You're nothing like her.

408
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:55,540
How am I different?

409
00:28:56,510 --> 00:28:57,970
You're here in front of me,

410
00:29:00,380 --> 00:29:01,380
alive.

411
00:29:06,150 --> 00:29:07,150
So,

412
00:29:08,280 --> 00:29:11,550
don't worry about
what anyone else says.

413
00:29:12,190 --> 00:29:13,690
And don't get hung up on...

414
00:29:13,690 --> 00:29:15,490
whether you look like someone
or not.

415
00:29:16,260 --> 00:29:18,530
Because you are, plain and simple,

416
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:20,600
Chloe.

417
00:29:30,570 --> 00:29:31,640
Wait for me.

418
00:29:38,850 --> 00:29:41,220
That must be Chloe,
the one Dan Hui brought in.

419
00:29:52,700 --> 00:29:53,700
Oh, no!

420
00:29:55,830 --> 00:29:56,830
Are you okay?

421
00:29:57,470 --> 00:29:58,670
Seriously?

422
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:00,670
My hand slipped.

423
00:30:02,440 --> 00:30:03,440
I'm so sorry.

424
00:30:04,670 --> 00:30:05,680
It's fine.

425
00:30:08,780 --> 00:30:10,250
But your shoes are
completely soaked.

426
00:30:12,080 --> 00:30:13,220
Are you going to keep them on?

427
00:30:16,050 --> 00:30:18,120
You should probably take them off.

428
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:21,720
Unless...

429
00:30:23,230 --> 00:30:25,360
there's a reason
you can't take them off?

430
00:31:11,910 --> 00:31:14,840
(Pearl in Red)

431
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:16,080
What do you two think you're doing?

432
00:31:16,080 --> 00:31:18,210
She's not Baek Jin Ju.

433
00:31:18,210 --> 00:31:19,780
Stop treating her like she is.

434
00:31:19,920 --> 00:31:23,950
He was irresponsible and cowardly,
right to the very end.

435
00:31:24,050 --> 00:31:26,760
After brutally murdering my father,

436
00:31:26,760 --> 00:31:28,660
you call him a coward
and irresponsible?

437
00:31:29,130 --> 00:31:32,200
If you were planning a shoot,
you should've cleared it first.

438
00:31:32,260 --> 00:31:36,700
But this shoot had to be today.
Right, Dad?

439
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:40,200
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
